{"tid":1154333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥張建宗評分支持率淨值跌至上任以來新低","createTime":"2019-05-14T08:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T10:35:04.000Z","uid":141151,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0a94a80750774a1e7e97e7265e70238f61fa4977","tid":1154333,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:30:24.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥張建宗評分支持率淨值跌至上任以來新低<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457476-20190514.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457476-20190514.htm&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZx%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=b4657fe3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457476-20190514.htm&h=9d8bd4eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457476-20190514.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n港大民研最新調查顯示，行政長官林鄭月娥及政務司司長張建宗的評分和支持率淨值，是他們上任以來新低。<br />\n<br />\n調查在本月初進行，林鄭月娥的評分是44.3分，比兩星期前顯著下跌4.7分，最新支持率為32%，反對率為56%，民望淨值明顯下跌12個百分點至負24。<br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗的評分是43.5分，支持率為23%，反對率為29%，民望淨值為負6個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n至於律政司司長鄭若驊，評分亦再創上任以來新低，比一個月前顯著下跌4.7分至29.5分；她的支持率為11%，反對率為52%，民望淨值比一個月前顯著下跌11個百分點至負41%。"},{"pid":"64bb9b0efde03f3e03dee63bf69e781c780dc3b1","tid":1154333,"uid":39365,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:35:50.000Z","msg":"無所謂啦, 反正就算幾低, 都唔會落台, D人又繼續返工"},{"pid":"a5c48d61fba3eeab43a3cc67841acc2e1ca199cb","tid":1154333,"uid":228963,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:37:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ed35d53e9d64a49ea4986f20c88eb3c37b98202","tid":1154333,"uid":50889,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:38:19.000Z","msg":"無所謂啦佢又唔係為市民服務"},{"pid":"0641b970f11112d441bafd89633e5c58818c8851","tid":1154333,"uid":24730,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:38:33.000Z","msg":"民望越低刁种越鍾意"},{"pid":"40c58bf4607534d6f9a644d